# Privacy Policy – HBF Add-on

HBF Add-on is a Google Sheets add-on that reads data from the active
spreadsheet and creates a Google Document based on user input.

## Data Access
The add-on accesses:
- Google Sheets data in the currently active spreadsheet
- Google Docs for the purpose of creating a document

## Data Usage
- Data is used only to provide the add-on’s functionality
- Data is processed temporarily during execution
- No data is stored, logged, sold, or shared with third parties

## Data Storage
HBF Add-on does not store any user data outside of the user’s Google
account.

## Third Parties
No data is shared with third-party services.

